stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> NotInstalled
    NotInstalled --> Installing: POST /enable or /init
    Installing --> Started: Resources created
    Started --> Stopped: POST /stop
    Stopped --> Started: POST /start
    Started --> Started: Running (tasks active)
    Started --> Error: Resource failure
    Error --> Started: Auto-recovery / manual restart
    Started --> Deleting: DELETE /engines
    Stopped --> Deleting: DELETE /engines
    Deleting --> NotInstalled: Cleanup complete
